        fame = 'Abyssea',
        fame_level = '3',
        title = nil,
        repeatable = 'Yes',
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'Only one Refuel and Replenish or A Mightier Martello quest can be completed per Vana\'dielian day, regardless of Abyssea area.\n1. Speak to the Machine Outfitter (Altepa) near the entrance of zone, and choose "Assist with upgrades" to accept the quest.\n   - You will obtain a [Key Item] Fuel reservoir.\n   - You cannot zone at any point during the quest, or you lose the key item and you must restart.\n2. Find a Martello in the zone. They are usually around the various Confluxes, or you can see a list on the Martello page.\n   - It is possible to upgrade it even if it is already at 100%.\n3. Click on "Prepare to upgrade martello" in the menu once you interact with one, then confirm.\n4. The log will tell you a direction to stand in order to upgrade the device, but the menu will tell you a different direction. Best results are achieve by following the direction in the menu.\n   - Although it is not in the log, the [Key Item] Fuel reservoir will be replaced with the [Key Item] Cracked fuel reservoir.\n5. Return to the Machine Outfitter (Altepa) to complete the quest.',
