        description = 'An enthusiastic researcher is on the verge of a discovery that might restore potable water to the inlet... for certain this time! Retrieve plant samples from the vicinity of the ponds, that his labors might at long last bear fruit.',
        reward = 'First time completion: 400 Cruor\nSubsequent completions: 200 Cruor\nChance at at one of the following Empyrean Armor +1 Hands seal.\nGoetia Seal: Feet (BLM)\nIga Seal: Feet (NIN)\nLancer\'s Seal: Feet (DRG)\nNavarch\'s Seal: Feet (COR)',
