        reward = 'Stearc Subligar with random  Augments\nChance at one of the following Empyrean Armor +1 Body seals:\nOrison Seal: Body (WHM)\nBale Seal: Body (DRK)\nFerine Seal: Body (BST)\nAoidos\' Seal: Body (BRD)\nNavarch\'s Seal: Body (COR)',
