            'Scars of Abyssea (Quest)',
            'Heroes of Abyssea',
        },
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'This quest automatically is flagged after completing the previous quest, The Truth Beckons.\n1. Before progressing, you must obtain a new [Key Item] Traverser stone from Joachim. You will need to wait until his restock timer is up.\n2. Examine any of the following Cavernous Maws to begin the corresponding quests.\n   - This can be done if you have the 1 hour lockout from the last quest but still have a Traverser Stone.\n   - After flagging one of these quests, you unlock the ability to teleport to the corresponding maw for a fee of 200 Cruor.\n   - Teleportation can be done via these abyssea maw teleportation NPCs.\n3. You must complete any three of these sub-quests to proceed with the next main Abyssea quest.\nVision of Abyssea\n4. Examine the Cavernous Maw in Konschtat Highlands at (I-12) to start the quest To Paste a Peiste.\n   - Survival Guide in North Gustaberg is close.\n5. Examine the Cavernous Maw in Tahrongi Canyon at (H-12) for the quest Megadrile Menace.\n   - Unity Wanted Battle lv.99 to Tahrongi Canyon is close.\n6. Examine the Cavernous Maw in La Theine Plateau at (E-4) for the quest A Goldstruck Gigas.\n   - Survival Guide in West Ronfaure is close.\nScars of Abyssea\n7. Examine the Cavernous Maw in Jugner Forest at (J-8) to start the quest the quest The Beast of Bastore.\n   - Survival Guide in Jugner Forest is close.\n8. Examine the Cavernous Maw in Buburimu Peninsula at (F-7) for the quest A Fluttery Fiend.\n   - Survival Guide in Buburimu Peninsula is close.\n9. Examine the Cavernous Maw in Valkurm Dunes at (I-9) for the quest A Delectable Demon.\n   - Survival Guide in Valkurm Dunes is close.\nHeroes of Abyssea\n10. Examine the Cavernous Maw in Xarcabard at (H-8) to start the quest the quest A Man-eating Mite.\n   - Survival Guide in Xarcabard is close.\n11. Examine the Cavernous Maw in North Gustaberg at (G-6) for the quest An Ulcerous Uragnite.\n   - Survival Guide in Oldton Movalpolos is close.\n12. Examine the Cavernous Maw in South Gustaberg at (J-10) for the quest A Beaked Blusterer.\n   - Home Point #1 in Bastok Mines is close.',
