        title = nil,
        repeatable = 'Yes',
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = {
            {name = '[Key Item] Frosted snoll reflector', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = '1. Talk to Guilboire (A) at (F-7) (Conflux #7) to begin this quest.\n2. He will provide you with two key items, the [Key Item] Snoll reflector and [Key Item] Experiment cheat sheet.\n3. Walk north to (G-5) and find the Impact Point location.\n4. The Notorious Monster Frost Bomb Mk-II will spawn to the west.\n5. Run up and attack it, which will raise its HP. Your goal is to raise its HP to at least 50%. The higher it is, the more Cruor reward you receive.\n6. Pull it towards the Impact Point. It will use Hypothermal Combustion regardless of its current TP. This will deal damage to the point, but not to you.\n   - If you disengage, you will fail this quest. This makes Trust Magic more difficult to use if they pull hate.\n7. Examine the Impact Point to receive a [Key Item] Frosted snoll reflector.\n   - If in a party, all players can receive the [Key Item] Frosted snoll reflector from the same Frost Bomb Mk-II as long as they click the Impact Point before it uses Hypothermal Combustion.\n8. Return and speak to Guilboire (A) for your reward.\n   - 25 completions of this quest will max fame in this zone.\nZoning is required in order to repeat this quest.',
        notes = nil,
    },
