        start_zone = 'Attohwa',
        start_pos = 'G-10',
        description = 'An astute alchemist has concluded that the miasmas seeping up through fissures in the ground are contributing to the tainted air. Follow the recipe he entrusted to you to synthesize the counteragent, test it on a miasma, then report back with your findings.',
