        fame = 'Abyssea',
        fame_level = '1',
        title = nil,
        repeatable = 'Yes',
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'Only one Refuel and Replenish or A Mightier Martello quest can be completed per Vana\'dielian day, regardless of Abyssea area.\n1. Speak to the Machine Outfitter (Altepa) near the entrance of zone, and choose "Assist with replenishment" to accept the quest.\n2. You will receive [Key Item] Vat of martello fuel.\n   - You cannot zone at any point during the quest, or you lose the key item and you must restart.\n3. Find a Martello in the zone. They are usually around the various Confluxes, or you can see a list on the Martello page.\n   - It is possible to replenish it even if it is already at 100% health.\n4. Click on "Prepare to replenish martello" in the menu once you interact with one, then confirm.\n5. The log will tell you a direction to stand in order to replenish the device, but the menu will tell you a different direction. Best results are achieve by following the direction in the menu.\n   - Although not told to you, the [Key Item] Vat of martello fuel is replaced with an [Key Item] Empty fuel vat.\n6. Report to the Machine Outfitter (Altepa) to complete the quest.',
