        description = 'The resistance\'s supply of linkshells has dwindled to dangerously low levels. Retrieve three from the field before your addle-minded client forgets just what exactly he asked you for.',
        reward = 'Black Earring /   Darkness Earring\nFirst time completion: 1,200 Cruor\nSubsequent completions: 600 Cruor\nChance at at one of the following Empyrean Armor +1 Feet seal.\nCirque Seal: Feet (PUP)\nEstoqueur\'s Seal: Feet (RDM)\nSylvan Seal: Feet (RNG)\nBale Seal: Feet (DRK)',
