        start_pos = 'G-7',
        description = 'Chumimi\'s good-for-nothing assistants Chemioue, Biggorf, and Tapoh Lihzeh still haven\'t done their homework. Hunt them down and relay their findings to Chumimi by any means necessary.',
        reward = 'First time completion: 400~500 Cruor\nSubsequent completions: 150~250 Cruor\nChance at one of the following Empyrean Armor +1 Body seals (ONLY if you do well with the quest):\nMavi Seal: Body (BLU)\nEstoqueur\'s Seal: Body (RDM) \nSylvan Seal: Body (RNG) \nCirque Seal: Body (PUP) \nRavager\'s Seal: Body (WAR)',
