        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Titus (A) at (G-11), at Conflux #5, to begin the quest.\n2. He will request a clump of Windurstian Tea Leaves.\n   - Titus (A) synthesizes the [Key Item] Bottle of military ink, but this item is only used during the cutscene and is not given to you.\n3. After trading him the leaves, he provides you with a [Key Item] Military ink package.\n4. Deliver the package to Chumimi (A) at the Oasis near Revelation Rock, (G-7).\n   - The closest conflux is #7.\n5. After delivering the package, you will complete the quest.',
