        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Miageau (A) at (L-11), Veridical Conflux #06, to begin the quest.\n2. You will receive the following four key items:\n   - [Key Item] Vial of purification agent (blk.)\n   - [Key Item] Vial of purification agent (brz.)\n   - [Key Item] Vial of purification agent (slv.)\n   - [Key Item] Vial of purification agent (gld.).\n3. Examine the 4 Murky Pond targetable locations in Abyssea - La Theine at (L-10), (K-11), and 2 at (H-7). These are the bodies of water you can see on your map.\n   - With each pond examined, your key items will be replaced with:\n     - [Key Item] Black-labeled vial\n     - [Key Item] Bronze-labeled vial\n     - [Key Item] Silver-labeled vial\n     - [Key Item] Gold-labeled vial.\n4. Return to Miageau (A) to complete the quest.\nZoning is required to repeat this quest.',
