        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Peshi Yohnts (A) at (F-9) in the Western Encampment. Veridical Conflux #03 is nearby.\n   - You\'ll need to speak to Kupipi (A) at (H-12) beforehand if you\'ve never done so before.\n2. She\'ll give you a Pickaxe and asks you to excavate a Hardened Bone from Excavation Points, or purchased on the Auction House.\n   - She\'ll only give you one so any extras from failure or repeating the quest will require your to bring own.\n3. Excavation Points are located at (E-5), scattered around the dragon skeleton. This is a little walk from Veridical Conflux #06.\n   - Mine until you find a Hardened Bone; multiple bones can be mined in a single session.\n   - Various other junk can be obtained rather than the Hardened Bone. There is a respawn timer on the Excavation Points.\n4. Trade Peshi Yohnts (A) a Hardened Bone to complete the quest.\n   - Note as soon as you engage her to repeat the quest a second time, it automatically is flagged in the quest log.\n   - 50 quest completions will max fame in this zone.\nZoning is required to repeat this quest.',
